trans-unit.source: Defines a mouse input gesture that can be used to invoke a command.
trans-unit.target: Definierar en mus inkommande gest som kan användas för att anropa ett kommando.

trans-unit.source: Unlike a <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyGesture>, a <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseAction> does not have to be paired with <xref:System.Windows.Input.ModifierKeys> to be a valid MouseGesture.
trans-unit.target: Till skillnad från en <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyGesture>, en <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseAction>behöver inte kombineras med <xref:System.Windows.Input.ModifierKeys>ska vara en giltig MouseGesture.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ModifierKeys> </xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseAction> </xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyGesture>

trans-unit.source: A MouseGesture can be bound to a <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand> (or other <xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand> implementations) through a <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding> so that the command is invoked when the MouseGesture occurs.
trans-unit.target: En MouseGesture kan bindas till en <xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>(eller andra <xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand>implementeringar) via en <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding>så att kommandot anropas när MouseGesture inträffar.</xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding> </xref:System.Windows.Input.ICommand> </xref:System.Windows.Input.RoutedCommand>

trans-unit.source: For MouseGesture [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] attribute usages, the property that is generally set in [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] is <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.Gesture%2A>, in cases where the gesture can represent both a mouse action and one or more modifier key.
trans-unit.target: För MouseGesture [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] attributet användningsområden, som vanligtvis har angetts i egenskapen [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] är <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.Gesture%2A>, i fall där en gest kan representera både en åtgärd och en eller flera låstangent.</xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.Gesture%2A>

trans-unit.source: You can also set the <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.Gesture%2A> property to be just a mouse action.
trans-unit.target: Du kan också ange den <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.Gesture%2A>egenskapen ska bara en åtgärd.</xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.Gesture%2A>

trans-unit.source: In general, it is recommended that you use only the <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyBinding.Gesture%2A> attribute from [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], rather than setting <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.MouseAction%2A>, even if you do not specify modifiers.
trans-unit.target: I allmänhet det rekommenderas att du använder bara den <xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyBinding.Gesture%2A>-attributet från [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)], i stället för inställningen <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.MouseAction%2A>, även om du inte anger modifierare.</xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.MouseAction%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Input.KeyBinding.Gesture%2A>

trans-unit.source: This will avoid ambiguity, provides the most streamlined syntax, and provides the most straightforward representation for serialization.
trans-unit.target: Detta kommer att undvika tvetydighet, ger den mest effektiva syntaxen och ger den enklaste representationen för serialisering.

trans-unit.source: MouseGesture [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] object element usages are possible but uncommon, because you can ordinarily set the <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.Gesture%2A> property of <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding> inline without the use of property element syntax.
trans-unit.target: MouseGesture [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xaml](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xaml-md.md)] objekt elementet användningsområden är möjliga men ovanliga, eftersom du normalt kan ange den <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.Gesture%2A>egenskapen för <xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding>infogade utan att använda egenskapselementsyntax.</xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding> </xref:System.Windows.Input.MouseBinding.Gesture%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Input.ModifierKeys> is a bit field enumeration, so it is possible for multiple modifier keys to be pressed at the same time.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Input.ModifierKeys>är lite fältet uppräkning, så är det möjligt för flera modifieraren nycklar till tryckt på samma gång.</xref:System.Windows.Input.ModifierKeys>

trans-unit.source: Use bit operations to determine the exact set of modifier keys pressed.
trans-unit.target: Använd bitars åtgärder att fastställa en exakt uppsättning modifierare nycklar trycks ned.
